    v1 = wp.exp((v0 * (tmp + 0.92 / v0 + 0.93)))
    v0 = (((tmp + 0.83 - v2 + 0.23) + 0.65) - (wp.abs(v1 + 0.58) * v1))
    tmp = (((tmp + 0.66 * v0 + 0.70) + wp.cos(tmp + 0.34)) / 0.95)
